CFS Scheduler Commands

CFS Scheduler Telemetry CFS Scheduler Table Definitions CFS Scheduler Configuration Parameters

The following is a list of Commands that are processed by the CFS Scheduler Application.

Global SCH_NOOP_CC
Scheduler No-Op

Global SCH_RESET_CC
Scheduler Reset Counters

Global SCH_ENABLE_CC
Enable Schedule Table Entry

Global SCH_DISABLE_CC
Disable Schedule Entry

Global SCH_ENABLE_GROUP_CC
Enable Group and/or Multi-Groups of Schedule Activities

Global SCH_DISABLE_GROUP_CC
Disable Group and/or Multi-Groups of Schedule Activities

Global SCH_ENABLE_SYNC_CC
Enable Major Frame Synchronization

Global SCH_SEND_DIAG_TLM_CC
Telemeter Scheduler Diagnostic Packet
